{"tid":1657752,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［影相撚］由瀑布灣公園行到去沙灣","createTime":"2019-10-16T08:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:50:34.000Z","uid":205704,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a43430481941967639b9b1171105967d21bc050b","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"好耐都無試過一邊行一影相喇<br />\n一來呢幾個月大家發夢都攰喇<br />\n二來唔係日日天氣都好<br />\n<br />\n發現距離上次影已經過咗好耐<br />\n［影相撚］由西環影去三家村<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1121137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1121137</a><br />\n<br />\n之前講過想圍住港島行一圈<br />\n我今日就由瀑布灣公園開始行<br />\n慢慢慢慢行完佢<br />\n希望終有一日會行得哂<br />\n<br />\n首先由華富邨落車行過去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OknHTyK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOknHTyK.jpg&h=9e495899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JqKnsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JqKnsf.jpg&h=8deec97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為大西北人<br />\n對呢頭真係完全唔熟<br />\n感覺呢到係好似一個老人邨<br />\n周圍都勁多老人家<br />\n<br />\n然後行幾步就係公園範圍<br />\n行落小小就可以望到海了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dUVeKGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdUVeKGo.jpg&h=f3cdd590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTEWdzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTEWdzR.jpg&h=f712915c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4067bcc7a942ebb2f923dd839ecdf29c6ac2bddb","tid":1657752,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"66498c0e25523dba88b9cd5f7b41080f25a82a3f","tid":1657752,"uid":8727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"gogogo"},{"pid":"76018a915ba6c82ea8e6a283c5bb29abcac2df03","tid":1657752,"uid":239353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"圖呢樓主?????????<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 被消失?"},{"pid":"9fd4e63afbd73cfd15394bdf786860da098808b2","tid":1657752,"uid":36012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"樓主行左好耐<br />\n係時候上來報個平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7bf94c5a88f77b6418d8790e81d45920ac0f53","tid":1657752,"uid":232687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7051c4f3a4067bbdf91621e66aa346032ea15a00","tid":1657752,"uid":324427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:42:08.000Z","msg":"樓主安全嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2890c28b7e43b50d081a8ba9a00e7ac3620c9a08","tid":1657752,"uid":40200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7051c4f3a4067bbdf91621e66aa346032ea15a00","tid":1657752,"uid":324427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:42:08.000Z","msg":"樓主安全嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"睇蒞要揼西瓜"},{"pid":"49d84acf99447e75dc472fc7687e46a02d720a43","tid":1657752,"uid":8727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"冇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3737b38128c0af7b6019c84f25e154929d616625","tid":1657752,"uid":233904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"瀑布灣好猛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e927d9483354c775cc954a5bff68273a117c0122","tid":1657752,"uid":70977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:11:05.000Z","ms