hread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"c47e0e7f439c660acca33fc04155a18b11924faf","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"個一日記得係3點幾先去到華富邨<br />\n搞到行嘅時間其實已經唔多<br />\n<br />\n望完一陣海之後就沿住公園去準備睇瀑布<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZfsihs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZfsihs.jpg&h=2553f508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgQG7aO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgQG7aO.jpg&h=0ddfcf6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xN1nRCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxN1nRCu.jpg&h=f883b5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bf72Kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bf72Kb.jpg&h=1598a4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途無咩人<br />\n唔太熱又對住個海 超級寫意舒服。"},{"pid":"ab407142672965224a68378032d41555da13247a","tid":1657752,"uid":8727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"繼續繼續<br />\n香港有冇咩攝影好路線推介"},{"pid":"97feed9185d15e51026e60e4292197b14e457079","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab407142672965224a68378032d41555da13247a","tid":1657752,"uid":8727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"繼續繼續<br />\n香港有冇咩攝影好路線推介"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"我都無...<br />\n我都想各位巴打介紹下，<br />\n最理想係近海 又唔係好多人去嘅"},{"pid":"3c90cadd6956e05703e96633d7403a9f17606a80","tid":1657752,"uid":253163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"有無去到沙灣個鞦韆？"},{"pid":"53a6658a7c9a43e113b0bf16faa1f9d915a55d0e","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c90cadd6956e05703e96633d7403a9f17606a80","tid":1657752,"uid":253163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"有無去到沙灣個鞦韆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"有啊！未寫到！"},{"pid":"f9e732a2f1195534279d2c63a2d9b7b07c7cdede","tid":1657752,"uid":264709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"相幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6e4504753cf757d158a4959850fd5e5829142f","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"行到公園嘅盡頭，<br />\n之後就見到一條好似封左 但其實有第二條路可以行落去嘅樓梯，<br />\n之後就到左瀑布灣了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysnuxRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysnuxRU.jpg&h=fc53f80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到個阿叔係個到玩石仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWnVtqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWnVtqd.jpg&h=e5c2dcc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXTYrbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXTYrbV.jpg&h=72b33a96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為仲有地方想要去，<br />\n影左一陣之後就走咗了"},{"pid":"3fa810a50102b7d4e40f6e97a0bf25c5b486dbc3","tid":1657752,"uid":205704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e732a2f1195534279d2c63a2d9b7b07c7cdede","tid":1657752,"uid":264709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"相幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"多謝你！"},{"pid":"9837440d06c6903b8585580e4f8ad73bd3bac9a3","tid":1657752,"uid":147029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"用咩機影， d色都係自己tune？"},{"pid":"c10c5b00508bad97dac0213c8a6199488756ca23","tid":1657752,"uid":3619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\